Display clear.
Workspace fileOutClassNamed: 'Display'.
Workspace setContents: 'RecorzKernelClass: #Display descriptorOrder: 2 objectKindOrder: 1 sourceBootOrder: 1 instanceVariableNames: ''''
!
defaultForm
    ^Display defaultForm
!
clear
    Display defaultForm clear.
    ^self
!
writeString: text
    Display defaultForm writeString: text.
    ^self
!
newline
    Transcript show: ''KEDIT''.
    Transcript cr.
    ^self
!'.
Workspace acceptCurrent.
Workspace reopen.
Display newline.
